<p>
  <span class="nym">Severin</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A derivative of <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>Severus</i>, a Roman <i>gens</i>, from <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>severus</i> 'serious, grave'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of two 5th C saints, a 6th C saint, and a 7th C pope.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


